== 車站概要 ==
{{multiple image|align=right|direction=vertical|width=220
|image1=201704 Concourse of Yanqiao Station.jpg|caption1=站厅
|image2=201704 Platform of Yanqiao Station.jpg|caption2=堰橋站月臺
|image3=201704 WXM L1 Trains at Yanqiao.jpg|caption3=预留的[[锡澄城际轨道交通|锡澄城际轨道交通]]轨道，现为折返线
